[normal]Written evidence from Bernard Jenkin MP, Chair of the Public Administration Select Committee (PASC)[bold]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]Thank you for your letter of 16 December 2013. I have discussed it with my 
[normal]Committee. Select Committees should be able to adapt to whatever the constitutional arrangements are. These arrangements should not be determined by the needs or wishes of select committees. 
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]January 2014
